App settings you need (portal → Function App → Configuration)
	•	ServiceBusConnection = connection string from Service Bus Namespace → Shared access policies (Policy with Send rights; e.g., RootManageSharedAccessKey or a custom “SendOnly” policy).
	•	ServiceBusEntity     = queue name (or topic name if you switch).
	•	Optional:
	•	UseSessions = true or false (must match whether the queue/topic is session‑enabled).
	•	Duplicate detection is enabled on the queue/topic itself (portal setting).

